{"TopicId":197472,"ForumId":29,"TopicTitle":"How to determine if the game window is foreground, minimized, etc?","CreatedByName":"Xyphos","CreatedById":139010,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-14T04:43:51Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Xyphos","CreatedById":139010,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-14T04:43:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nneed a solid way to determine if the game window is active in the foreground, minimized, fullscreen, etc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ValiZockt","CreatedById":197053,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-14T07:08:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo determine if game is focused or paused you can use the\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://docs.unity3d.com/ScriptReference/MonoBehaviour.OnApplicationFocus.html\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EMonobehaviour.OnApplicationFocus\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0\u0026amp;\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://docs.unity3d.com/ScriptReference/MonoBehaviour.OnApplicationPause.html\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EMonobehaviour.OnApplicationPaused\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0callbacks\u00A0(there\u2019s also two GameEvents onGamePaused \u0026amp; onGameUnpaused)\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo check if you\u2019re in fullscreen you can use\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalspaceprogram.com/api/class_game_settings.html#ad097f0c8accb695509afa35d110a06d8\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EGameSettings.FULLSCREEN\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xyphos","CreatedById":139010,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-14T10:09:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCheers!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}